description: Greenland No. 1 Down Parka has all the classic details – plus a slightly longer cut. Based on the popular Greenland No. 1 Down Jacket but with extra warmth over the rear and thighs. It is also slightly roomier so there is plenty of space for insulating layers underneath. A versatile everyday favourite for the colder months, made in durable G-1000 Eco and padded with fluffy, warm down.
name: Fjallraven Greenland No. 1 Down Parka - Mens
